Puak Syaitan berada di belakang saya.

85
00:06:53,795 --> 00:06:55,154
Biarpun kalah, saya mesti berjuang.

86
00:06:59,075 --> 00:06:59,674
Ya.

87
00:07:00,154 --> 00:07:00,994
