untuk menyelamatkan orang.

95
00:07:23,075 --> 00:07:23,674
Jing Jian!

96
00:07:24,795 --> 00:07:25,554
Awak gila?

97
00:07:26,035 --> 00:07:27,355
Tergamak awak menolong Puak Syaitan?

98
00:07:28,475 --> 00:07:29,114
Abang,

99
00:07:29,554 --> 00:07:30,234
berundurlah.

100
00:07:30,834 --> 00:07:31,755
Jangan paksa saya bertindak.

101
00:07:32,195 --> 00:07:34,274
Dewa Syaitan
mengacau-bilaukan Cang Qiong.

102
00:07:34,875 --> 00:07:36,954
Tidak dapat patah balik antara
Puak Betara dan Puak Syaitan.

103
