135
00:09:15,515 --> 00:09:16,794
Saya nak membunuh Tian Qi dan Hou Chi

136
00:09:17,075 --> 00:09:18,434
di majlis perkahwinan.

137
00:09:19,275 --> 00:09:20,794
Namun sebaliknya,

138
00:09:21,075 --> 00:09:22,875
